          <title>Alex Ovechkin scores 884th goal to move 10 back of tying Wayne Gretzky's NHL career record</title>
          <description><![CDATA[WASHINGTON (AP) — Alex Ovechkin scored the 884th goal of his NHL career late in the Washington Capitals' 3-1 loss to the red-hot Tampa Bay Lightning on Saturday, moving 10 away from tying Wayne Gretzky’s record.]]></description>
